ttps:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/meo-thiet-ke-card-visit.html\/#5_Can_nhac_viec_thiet_ke_Series_Card_Visit\" title=\"5. C\u00e2n nh\u1eafc vi\u1ec7c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf Series Card Visit\">5. C\u00e2n nh\u1eafc vi\u1ec7c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf Series Card Visit<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/meo-thiet-ke-card-visit.html\/#6_Chu_trong_vao_logo_cua_doanh_nghiep\" title=\"6. Ch\u00fa tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0o logo c\u1ee7a doanh nghi\u1ec7p\">6. Ch\u00fa tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0o logo c\u1ee7a doanh nghi\u1ec7p<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/meo-thiet-ke-card-visit.html\/#7_Dieu_cuoi_cung_Luon_sang_tao\" title=\"7. \u0110i\u1ec1u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng: Lu\u00f4n s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o!\">7. \u0110i\u1ec1u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng: Lu\u00f4n s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o!<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p><strong>Card visit<\/strong> l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u b\u1ea1n, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n trao \u0111\u1ed5i card.<\/p>\n<p>N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 b\u1ea1n \u0111ang t\u00ednh <strong>thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf card visit<\/strong> cho c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c kinh doanh \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, ho\u1eb7c thay \u0111\u1ed5i m\u1eabu card visit c\u0169, th\u00ec d\u01b0\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i xin <strong>b\u1eadt m\u00ed 7 m\u1eb9o thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf Card Visit \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t 2020 <\/strong>\u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n tham kh\u1ea3o.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"7_Meo_nho_de_thiet_ke_Card_Visit\"><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 110%; color: #0000ff;\"><strong>7 M\u1eb9o nh\u1ecf \u0111\u1ec3 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf Card Visit<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"1_Thau_hieu_muc_dich_cua_card_visit\"><\/span><em><strong>1. Th\u1ea5u hi\u1ec3u m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch c\u1ee7a card visit<\/strong><\/em><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>D\u00f9 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 \u0111ang l\u00e0m v\u1ec1 ng\u00e0nh ngh\u1ec1 g\u00ec, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong <strong>thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf card visit <\/strong>ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i hi\u1ec3u\u00a0<strong>card visit<\/strong> ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n cho s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i gi\u1eefa c\u00f4ng ty c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n v\u00e0 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng. H\u00e3y \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c, b\u1ed1 c\u1ee5c s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi t\u1edbi ph\u1ea7n l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn m\u00e0u s\u1eafc v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2379\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2379\" style=\"width: 825px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-2379\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/m\u1eb9o-thi\u1ebft-k\u1ebf-card-vist.png\" alt=\"m\u1eb9o thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf card visit\" width=\"825\" height=\"627\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/m\u1eb9o-thi\u1ebft-k\u1ebf-card-vist.png 930w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/m\u1eb9o-thi\u1ebft-k\u1ebf-card-vist-300x228.png 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/m\u1eb9o-thi\u1ebft-k\u1ebf-card-vist-768x584.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 825px) 100vw, 825px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2379\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch truy\u1ec1n t\u1ea3i th\u00f4ng tin l\u00e0 m\u1eb9o \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ch\u00fang m\u00ecnh mu\u1ed1n chia s\u1ebb<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"2_Phan_biet_ro_rang_giua_ca_nhan_va_thuong_hieu\"><\/span><em><strong>2. Ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng gi\u1eefa c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u.<\/strong><\/em><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>N\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh card visit n\u00e0y l\u00e0 d\u00e0nh cho doanh nghi\u1ec7p, d\u00f9 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 doanh nghi\u1ec7p \u0111\u00f3, c\u0169ng tr\u00e1nh n\u00ean th\u00eam c\u00e1c s\u1edf th\u00edch c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, \u0111\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n l\u00ean tr\u00ean card visit.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2380\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2380\" style=\"width: 825px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-2380\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/card-visit-cho-c\u00e1-nh\u00e2n.jpg\" alt=\"m\u1eb9o thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf card visit cho c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n\" width=\"825\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/card-visit-cho-c\u00e1-nh\u00e2n.jpg 1200w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/card-visit-cho-c\u00e1-nh\u00e2n-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/card-visit-cho-c\u00e1-nh\u00e2n-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/card-visit-cho-c\u00e1-nh\u00e2n-1024x683.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 825px) 100vw, 825px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2380\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Card visit cho c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"3_Dat_diem_nhan_vao_thong_tin_quan_trong_nhat\"><\/span><em><strong>3. \u0110\u1eb7t \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n v\u00e0o th\u00f4ng tin quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t<\/strong><\/em><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0o m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1ec1 c\u00f4ng ty m\u00ecnh? B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 t\u00e1i c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng? Ban c\u00f3 v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u0103ng ch\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng? Li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ho\u1eb7c d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 n\u00e0o m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra m\u1eaft? B\u1ea1n v\u1eeba thay \u0111\u1ed5i s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 email c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh? H\u00e3y suy ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u00e2n b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n ch\u00fang tr\u00ean card visit c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2381\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2381\" style=\"width: 825px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-2381\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/nh\u1eefng-th\u00f4ng-tin-quan-tr\u1ecdng-c\u1ea7n-\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c-l\u00e0m-n\u1ed5i-tr\u1ed9i.jpg\" alt=\"m\u1eb9o thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf card visit\" width=\"825\" height=\"1407\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/nh\u1eefng-th\u00f4ng-tin-quan-tr\u1ecdng-c\u1ea7n-\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c-l\u00e0m-n\u1ed5i-tr\u1ed9i.jpg 564w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/nh\u1eefng-th\u00f4ng-tin-quan-tr\u1ecdng-c\u1ea7n-\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c-l\u00e0m-n\u1ed5i-tr\u1ed9i-176x300.jpg 176w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 825px) 100vw, 825px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2381\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m n\u1ed5i tr\u1ed9i<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"4_Tranh_thiet_ke_card_visit_giong_nhung_san_pham_cua_nguoi_khac\"><\/span><em><strong>4. Tr\u00e1nh thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf card visit gi\u1ed1ng nh\u1eefng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c.<\/strong><\/em><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>\u0110\u1eebng ng\u1ea1i vi\u1ec7c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 kh\u1ea3o s\u00e1t nh\u1ecf tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1eaft tay v\u00e0o thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf card visit. Vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vi\u1ec7c sao ch\u00e9p c\u00e1c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi b\u1eaft k\u1ecbp c\u00e1c xu h\u01b0\u1edbng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra. H\u01a1n th\u1ebf n\u1eefa, n\u00f3 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1i g\u00ec n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o card visit, c\u00e1i g\u00ec kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Xem th\u00eam: <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><em><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/huong-dan-thiet-ke-card-visit.html\/\">H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn chi ti\u1ebft thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf card visit\u00a0<\/a><\/em><\/span><\/strong><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"5_Can_nhac_viec_thiet_ke_Series_Card_Visit\"><\/span><em><strong>5. C\u00e2n nh\u1eafc vi\u1ec7c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf Series Card Visit<\/strong><\/em><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>C\u00e2n nh\u1eafc c\u00e1c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf card visit s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1ed9t series c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n ho\u1eb7c b\u1ed9 s\u01b0u t\u1eadp n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u01a1i g\u1ee3i s\u1ef1 t\u00f2 m\u00f2.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2382\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2382\" style=\"width: 825px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-2382\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/serie-card-visit-s\u1ebd-\u0111em-\u0111\u1ebfn-\u1ea5n-t\u01b0\u1ee3ng-cho-kh\u00e1ch-h\u00e0ng.jpg\" alt=\"card visit theo b\u1ed9\" width=\"825\" height=\"979\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/serie-card-visit-s\u1ebd-\u0111em-\u0111\u1ebfn-\u1ea5n-t\u01b0\u1ee3ng-cho-kh\u00e1ch-h\u00e0ng.jpg 574w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/serie-card-visit-s\u1ebd-\u0111em-\u0111\u1ebfn-\u1ea5n-t\u01b0\u1ee3ng-cho-kh\u00e1ch-h\u00e0ng-253x300.jpg 253w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 825px) 100vw, 825px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2382\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Serie card visit s\u1ebd \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"6_Chu_trong_vao_logo_cua_doanh_nghiep\"><\/span><em><strong>6. Ch\u00fa tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0o logo c\u1ee7a doanh nghi\u1ec7p<\/strong><\/em><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>\u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 <strong>thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf card visit \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00e0 b\u1eaft m\u1eaft <\/strong>th\u00ec b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u00ean logo c\u1ee7a doanh nghi\u1ec7p<strong>.<\/strong>\u00a0B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1ea5n v\u00e0o logo c\u1ee7a c\u00f4ng ty b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1eb7t ch\u00fang tr\u00ean m\u1ed9t m\u1eb7t ri\u00eang c\u1ee7a card visit.<\/p>\n<p>\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u d\u1ec5 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn di\u00ean v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi ch\u00fang t\u0103ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh trong c\u00e1c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf card visit c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean thu\u1ed9c c\u00f4ng ty. C\u00e0ng nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y logo c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n, h\u1ecd nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n ra ch\u00fang c\u00e0ng nhanh h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2383\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2383\" style=\"width: 825px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-2383\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/logo-n\u00ean-\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c-l\u00e0m-n\u1ed5i-b\u1eadt-tr\u00ean-card-visit.jpg\" alt=\"logo n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt tr\u00ean card visit\" width=\"825\" height=\"619\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/logo-n\u00ean-\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c-l\u00e0m-n\u1ed5i-b\u1eadt-tr\u00ean-card-visit.jpg 500w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/logo-n\u00ean-\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c-l\u00e0m-n\u1ed5i-b\u1eadt-tr\u00ean-card-visit-300x225.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 825px) 100vw, 825px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2383\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">logo n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt tr\u00ean card visit<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><strong>Xem th\u00eam: <a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/huong-dan-thiet-ke-card-visit.html\/\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><em>G\u1eedi b\u1ea1n 8 b\u01b0\u1edbc thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf Card Visit chu\u1ea9n c\u1ee7a n\u0103m 2020<\/em><\/span><\/a><\/strong><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"7_Dieu_cuoi_cung_Luon_sang_tao\"><\/span><strong>7. \u0110i\u1ec1u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng: Lu\u00f4n s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o!<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n th\u00eam t\u00ednh s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o v\u00e0o trong thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf card visit, h\u00e3y \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o r\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u hi\u1ec3u ch\u00fang v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 nh\u1ea7m l\u1eabn n\u00e0o c\u1ea3.<\/p>\n<p>B\u1ea1n n\u00ean l\u00e0m m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i ki\u1ec3m tra nh\u1ecf \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi xung quanh m\u00ecnh, r\u1ed3i sau \u0111\u00f3 m\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh li\u1ec7u \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng n\u00e0y c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 thi hay kh\u00f4ng.<\/p>\n<p>V\u1edbi <strong>7\u00a0m\u1eb9o thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf card visit<\/strong> tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y ch\u00fang m\u00ecnh mong r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho nh\u1eefng t\u1ea5m danh thi\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 doanh nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Card visit l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u b\u1ea1n, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n trao \u0111\u1ed5i card. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 b\u1ea1n \u0111ang t\u00ednh thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf card visit cho c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c kinh doanh \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, ho\u1eb7c thay \u0111\u1ed5i m\u1eabu card visit c\u0169, th\u00ec d\u01b0\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i xin b\u1eadt m\u00ed 7&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":2384,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[57],"tags":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO Premium plugin v18.7 (Yoast SEO v19.9) - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>B\u1eadt m\u00ed 7 M\u1eb9o thi\u1ebft k\u1ebft Card Visit kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ai c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft | \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"\u00c1 ch\u00e2u Media trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y xin chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n 7 m\u1eb9o thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf card visit \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 tin \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng cho nh\u1eefng t\u1ea5m danh thi\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/meo-thiet-ke-card-visit.html\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"vi_VN\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"B\u1eadt m\u00ed 7 m\u1eb9o thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf Card Visit \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t 2020\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"\u00c1 ch\u00e2u Media trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y xin chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n 7 m\u1eb9o thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf card visit \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1